graph LR
    RHODS[RHODS Operator<br/>v1.6.0-556-g9f2b32973]

    %% External Dependencies
    RHODS -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.23+]
    RHODS -->|enterprise platform| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.12+]
    RHODS -->|service mesh<br/>conditional for KServe| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Operator<br/>Maistra/Istio 2.x]
    RHODS -->|serverless<br/>conditional for KServe| Serverless[Serverless Operator<br/>Knative 1.x]
    RHODS -->|authorization<br/>conditional for KServe| Authorino[Authorino Operator 0.x]
    RHODS -.->|monitoring<br/>optional| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator 0.x]
    RHODS -.->|certificates<br/>optional| CertManager[cert-manager 1.x]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - Deployments
    RHODS -->|deploys| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    RHODS -->|deploys| Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Notebooks]
    RHODS -->|deploys| DSP[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Tekton/Argo]
    RHODS -->|deploys| KServe[KServe<br/>Model Serving]
    RHODS -->|deploys| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>Seldon-based]
    RHODS -->|deploys| CodeFlare[CodeFlare<br/>MCAD/InstaScale]
    RHODS -->|deploys| Ray[Ray<br/>Distributed Computing]
    RHODS -->|deploys| Kueue[Kueue<br/>Job Queueing]

    %% Component interdependencies
    KServe -->|requires| ServiceMesh
    KServe -->|requires| Serverless
    KServe -->|requires| Authorino

    %% CRD Management
    RHODS -->|manages CRs| DashboardCRs[OdhApplication<br/>OdhDocument<br/>AcceleratorProfile]
    RHODS -->|watches CRs| DSPCRs[DataSciencePipelinesApplication]
    RHODS -->|manages CRs| KServeCRs[InferenceService<br/>ServingRuntime<br/>ClusterServingRuntime]
    RHODS -->|watches CRs| RayCRs[RayCluster<br/>RayJob<br/>RayService]
    RHODS -->|watches CRs| CodeFlareCRs[AppWrapper<br/>QueueJob]
    RHODS -->|watches CRs| KueueCRs[Queue<br/>Workload]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|UI management| RHODS
    DSP -->|auto deploy models| KServe

    %% External Services
    RHODS -->|API operations| K8sAPIServer[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    RHODS -.->|build-time manifests<br/>devFlags| GitRepos[Component Git Repos<br/>odh-manifests<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    RHODS -->|image pulls| Registries[Container Registries<br/>registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Monitoring Integration
    PrometheusCluster[Prometheus<br/>Cluster Monitoring] -->|scrapes metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP| RHODS

